channel.title: Wow this is starting to make me mad
channel.description: It says that i've posted my server I've tried this on 4 different computers already switched to dedi and everything but when I TRY TO POST ON THE STATUS PAGE IT SAYS POSTED BUT NEVER POSTS WTF IS UP WITH THIS? I can't even get players on my server because the status page is down are my posts getting deleted on purpose or what I haven't done anything to anyone.
